# Screenshots Directory

This directory is used to store browser compatibility test screenshots for the white background display testing across mainstream browsers.

## Purpose
- Store screenshots from different browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, etc.)
- Document visual consistency of the white background implementation
- Track any rendering differences or compatibility issues
- Maintain visual regression testing records

## File Naming Convention
- `chrome_desktop.png` - Chrome browser on desktop
- `firefox_desktop.png` - Firefox browser on desktop  
- `safari_desktop.png` - Safari browser on desktop
- `edge_desktop.png` - Edge browser on desktop
- `chrome_mobile.png` - Chrome browser on mobile
- `firefox_mobile.png` - Firefox browser on mobile
- `safari_mobile.png` - Safari browser on mobile

## Test Focus Areas
- White background color rendering (`#ffffff`)
- Semi-transparent container background (`rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)`)
- Backdrop filter blur effect compatibility
- Box shadow rendering consistency
- Overall visual appearance across different browsers